                  W25Q64BVerase PROC
;;;1153   
;;;1154   static BOOL W25Q64BVerase(void)
000a30  e92d4070          PUSH     {r4-r6,lr}
;;;1155   {
;;;1156       int waitime = 20;

;;;1157       int waitCounter = 30;

;;;1158       int retryTime = 0;

;;;1159       W25Q64BVErase();

;;;1160

;;;1162       vTaskDelay(100/portTICK_RATE_MS);

000a54  ebfffffe          BL       vTaskDelay
;;;1163       do{
000a58  e1a00000          MOV      r0,r0
                  |L1.2652|
;;;1164           waitime = 20 - retryTime;

;;;1165           if(waitime <= 0)

;;;1166               waitime = 0;

                  |L1.2668|
;;;1167           terninalPrintf("W25Q64BV erasing,please wait %d second...\r",waitime);

000a70  e28f0f97          ADR      r0,|L1.3284|

                  |L1.2696|
;;;1170           retryTime++;
000a88  e2866001          ADD      r6,r6,#1
